description:
This piece is part of a series of mine (Chaotic Mind , 2022).

-

"I felt a tingling sensation in my head, and then everything went blank. I couldn't move or speak, and I started to feel panicked. What was going on? I tried to call out, but my voice was gone. I was surrounded by darkness, and I started to feel scared. I had never felt so lost before."

-

Abstract light-painting created with steel wool on fire in pitch darkness. It was complemented by digital art. 

*

'Brain Zaps VI', 2022
